# MDC authoring (this repo and targets)

## Frontmatter

```yaml
---
description: One line for the rule picker
alwaysApply: true   # OR omit and use globs:
globs: path/to/**,other/**
---
```

- **alwaysApply:** short conduct, safety, repo layout, skill workflow — keep lean.
- **globs:** host- or folder-specific detail (layer rules in app repos; `references/` here).

Valid fields per [Cursor Rules](https://cursor.com/docs/context/rules): `alwaysApply`, `description`, `globs` (and `paths` where supported). Do not rely on undocumented keys.

